short optional note for clarification)\n\nPDF export per user or summary\n\nFilter by date / party / type\n\n\n\n---\n\nPublic Tools & Pages\n\nCobb Rate (auto-post daily at 9 AM IST)\n\nBroiler Rate (auto-post)\n\nChick Rate (auto-post)\n\nFCR Calculator\n\nProfit Margin Calculator\n\nFeed Cost Estimator\n\nVaccine Reminder\n\nBatch Tracker\n\nDistrict-wise Rate Map (Bihar, Bengal, Jharkhand, UP)\n\nFarmer of the Month\n\nGovernment Schemes Info Page\n\nFarmer Discussion Wall (Forum-style)\n\nDesi Training Videos (YouTube Embedded)\n\n\n\n---", "skills": ["Artificial Intelligence", "CSS", "Artificial Intelligence", "CSS", "Database Administration", "Graphic Design", "HTML"], "ClientRating": 0.0, "ClientReviews": 0, "timestamp": "2025-07-27T17:00:28.055012+00:00"}
