{"url": "https://www.freelancer.in/projects/blockchain/usdt-flash-token-tron-blockchain.html", "title": "USDT Flash Token on Tron Blockchain", "budget": "Budget \u20b912,500 \u2013 37,500 INR", "parsed_budget": {"min": "12500", "max": "37500", "currency_symbol": "\u20b9", "currency": "INR", "per_hour": false}, "description": "Flash USDT Token Development on TRC20\n\nWe are planning to develop a custom Flash USDT token on the TRC20 (Tron) blockchain. This token will simulate USDT but with advanced, customizable smart contract functionalities.\n\nSmart Contract Development Requirements:\n\nWe need a smart contract with the following features:\n1. Transferability\n\u2022 Users can freely send and receive tokens between addresses.\n2. Spendability\n\u2022 Token holders can use tokens as a medium of exchange or payment with enabled spending functions.\n3. Direct Receipt\n\u2022 Recipients will receive tokens instantly upon transfer with on-chain confirmation.\n4. Split & Swap\n\u2022 Token amounts can be split into smaller values and optionally swapped with other TRC20 tokens or stablecoins (custom logic can define swap pairs).\n5. Multi-Wallet Support\n\u2022 The token should support multiple wallet addresses under the same identity for seamless internal transfers or access control.\n6. Time-Bound Validity\n\u2022 Option to assign an expiry date or time limit to tokens. After expiry, the tokens become non-transferable or burnable based on logic.\n7. Unlimited Transfers\n\u2022 No restrictions on how many times a token can be transferred, ensuring full liquidity and usability.\n\n\u2e3b\n\nPurpose:\n\nThis token will be useful for short-term payments, internal settlements, demos, or any environment where fast, flexible token operations are required \u2014 without affecting actual USDT supply.", "skills": ["Adobe Flash", "Blockchain", "Adobe Flash", "Blockchain", "Cryptocurrency", "Ethereum", "Java"], "ClientRating": 5.0, "ClientReviews": 22, "timestamp": "2025-07-27T17:04:20.995877+00:00"}
{"url": "https://www.freelancer.in/projects/web-development/poultry-help.html", "title": "Poultry Help", "budget": "Budget \u20b9600 \u2013 1,500 INR", "parsed_budget": {"min": "600", "max": "1500", "currency_symbol": "\u20b9", "currency": "INR", "per_hour": false}, "description": "Build Poultry Farmer & Dealer Portal with Accounting, Admin Panel, Auto Chick Rates\n\n\n---\n\nProject Overview\n\nWe need a complete poultry management website (ZIP-based) for ChickRate.com(I'll change it Later) , designed for rural farmers and dealers in Bihar, Bengal, and Jharkhand. The site will have dual dashboards (Farmer & Dealer), built-in accounting system, admin controls, chick rate auto-posting, tools like FCR, profit calculator, batch tracking, and more.\n\nNo heavy CMS like WordPress needed. Just a lightweight, clean, mobile-first portal with Hindi-English UI.\n\n\n---\n\nUser Roles & Permissions\n\nFarmer Dashboard\n\nProfile management\n\nBatch management\n\nVaccination alerts\n\nProfit calculator, feed estimator, FCR calculator\n\nAccounting Panel (credit/debit entries, PDF export)\n\nView own transactions\n\nView linked dealer (if added)\n\nCannot be deleted by dealer if self-registered\n\n\nDealer Dashboard\n\nAdd/Edit/Delete own-added farmers\n\nCannot delete self-registered farmers\n\nManage multiple:\n\nFeed Companies\n\nMedicine Companies\n\nTransportation Vendors\n\n\nDealer-side Accounting Panel (with filters, PDF export)\n\nAdd transactions (payments, feed, medicine)\n\nView all transaction summaries by farmer/date/type\n\n\nAdmin Dashboard\n\nAdd/Edit/Delete any dealer or farmer\n\nView all transactions\n\nFull database control\n\nDeleted data stays in backup for at least 7 days\n\nRestore or permanently delete records\n\nControl over chick rate posting\n\n\n\n---\n\nAccounting System Must Include\n\nParty name (Farmer or Dealer)\n\nDate\n\nType (Purchase, Payment, Feed, Medicine, Transport)\n\nDescription / Notes\n\nDebit / Credit / Balance tracking\n\nRemark (short optional note for clarification)\n\nPDF export per user or summary\n\nFilter by date / party / type\n\n\n\n---\n\nPublic Tools & Pages\n\nCobb Rate (auto-post daily at 9 AM IST)\n\nBroiler Rate (auto-post)\n\nChick Rate (auto-post)\n\nFCR Calculator\n\nProfit Margin Calculator\n\nFeed Cost Estimator\n\nVaccine Reminder\n\nBatch Tracker\n\nDistrict-wise Rate Map (Bihar, Bengal, Jharkhand, UP)\n\nFarmer of the Month\n\nGovernment Schemes Info Page\n\nFarmer Discussion Wall (Forum-style)\n\nDesi Training Videos (YouTube Embedded)\n\n\n\n---", "skills": ["Artificial Intelligence", "CSS", "Artificial Intelligence", "CSS", "Database Administration", "Graphic Design", "HTML"], "ClientRating": 0.0, "ClientReviews": 0, "timestamp": "2025-07-27T17:04:21.410516+00:00"}
