\n\nTimeline:\nProject must be completed with fully working system and clean documentation within 7 to 10 days.\n\nDeliverables:\n\nSQL schema\n\nExcel workbook with working VBA connection\n\nIntegrated Google Maps API functionality\n\nFinal .sql and .xlsm files\n\nStep-by-step documentation for ongoing use", "skills": ["API Development", "Data Analysis", "API Development", "Data Analysis", "Data Integration", "Database Management", "Excel"], "ClientRating": 5.0, "ClientReviews": 6, "timestamp": "2025-07-27T19:32:13.266171+00:00"}
