nditions*: Rules and regulations for using the platform like https://www.indianindustrialtutorial.in/terms-condition\n8. *FAQ*: Frequently Asked Questions and answers\n\n*User Management*\n\n1. *Login*: Secure login system for users and admins\n2. *Registration*: User registration process with email verification\n3. *User Profile*: User dashboard to manage account settings and activity\n4. *Forgot Password*: Password recovery process\n\n*Technical Requirements*\n\n1. *Platform*: WordPress\n2. *SEO-friendly*: Yes\n3. *Responsive*: Yes\n4. *Training*: Provide training to one of our team members for admin and front-end management\n\n*Deliverables*\n\n1. A fully functional learning and job portal\n2. A user-friendly admin panel for content management\n3. Secure payment gateway integration\n4. Training for admin and front-end management\n5. SEO-friendly and responsive design\n\n*Timeline and Milestones*\n\nTo be discussed and finalized with the development team.\n\n*Acceptance Criteria*\n\n1. The platform meets all the key features and technical requirements.\n2. The admin panel is user-friendly and functional.\n3. The platform is secure, SEO-friendly, and responsive.\n4. Training is provided to the designated team member.", "skills": ["SEO", "UI / User Interface", "SEO", "UI / User Interface", "Web Development", "Website Design", "WordPress"], "ClientRating": 0.0, "ClientReviews": 0, "timestamp": "2025-07-28T00:20:08.695150+00:00"}
