{"url": "https://www.freelancer.in/projects/php/whatsapp-automation-integration-with.html", "title": "**WhatsApp Automation Integration with Payment & Access Code System** -- 2", "budget": "Budget $30 \u2013 250 USD", "parsed_budget": {"min": "30", "max": "250", "currency_symbol": "$", "currency": "USD", "per_hour": false}, "description": "We are looking for a developer to help us integrate a WhatsApp-based automation system for our service ( WiFi). The system should allow users to interact with us via WhatsApp using simple commands and also make payments directly from WhatsApp.\n\n---\n\n### Key Features to Implement:\n\n1. **Auto-Response On First Message:**\n\n* When a user sends \u201cHi\u201d or any greeting, the system should auto-reply with a friendly welcome message and a menu of available commands.\n\nExample:\n\n```\nHi! Welcome to Chafinity WiFi\nHere's what you can do:\n1. Buy Internet Access\n2. Check Available Plans\n3. Make Payment\n4. Receive Access Code\n\nReply with:\n- #plans\n- #subscribe\n- #pay\n- #getcode\n- #help\n```\n\n2. **Payment Integration:**\n\n* Integrate **Paystack** for secure in-chat payments.\n* User selects a plan and receives a payment link.\n* Once payment is successful, proceed to the next step.\n\n3. **Access Code Generation:**\n\n* After successful payment, trigger an API from our system to automatically generate and send a WiFi access code back to the user on WhatsApp.\n\n4. **Leads Collection:**\n\n* Save basic lead information (like name and phone number) from every WhatsApp user that interacts with the bot, even if they don\u2019t complete a purchase.\n\n---\n\nAPIs to Integrate:\n\n1. **Paystack API** (for payments)\n2. **Internal API** (to fetch and send access codes after confirmed payment)\n\n---\n\nWhat You\u2019ll Deliver:\n\n* WhatsApp bot that handles user onboarding, payments, and code delivery.\n* Integration of both Paystack and our internal API.\n* Option to easily update response texts and commands later.\n*