{"url": "https://www.freelancer.in/projects/nodejs/custom-whatsapp-group-management-system.html", "title": "Custom WhatsApp Group Management System with Admin Dashboard, WhatsApp API, OCR Verification, Payments & Ad Slot Scheduling", "budget": "Budget \u20b91,500 \u2013 12,500 INR", "parsed_budget": {"min": "1500", "max": "12500", "currency_symbol": "\u20b9", "currency": "INR", "per_hour": false}, "description": "I need a **Custom Web Application** built with the following features:\n\n### \u2705 Core Features:\n1. **WhatsApp Group Link Tracking (State & District-wise):**\n- Add/manage multiple WhatsApp groups (State \u2192 District \u2192 Group).\n- Track members and auto-manage queue if the group is full.\n\n2. **Member Queue Management:**\n- Auto-check group limit (256 members) via WhatsApp API.\n- Add users to a waiting queue & auto-invite when slots open.\n\n3. **Screenshot Verification (OCR):**\n- Users upload group join proof screenshots.\n- OCR auto-verifies text (Group Name/Link) & stores logs.\n\n4. **Payment Tracking:**\n- Razorpay/Stripe integration.\n- Track payments (Pending/Paid/Failed) & auto-update database.\n\n5. **Automated WhatsApp Messaging:**\n- Via Meta WhatsApp API And Waziper API.\n- Auto-replies, group links, reminders, confirmations.\n\n---\n\n### \u2705 Add-On 1: Ad Slot Management\n- 8 Ad Slots per day per district.\n- Schedule and auto-send ads via WhatsApp API (between 9:30 AM\u201310 PM).\n- Enforce 30\u201360 min gap between brands.\n- Track ad delivery logs (Sent/Read).\n\n---\n\n### \u2705 Add-On 2: WhatsApp API Settings Panel\n- Admin can set:\n- API key/token (Meta Cloud or Waziper).\n- Sender numbers.\n- Approved templates (Meta API).\n\n---\n\n### \u2705 Admin Dashboard:\n- Group Management (Add/Edit/Delete, view member counts)\n- User Management (State/District filter)\n- Screenshot Verification Logs\n- Payments (Filter by status/district)\n- Ad Slot Scheduler\n- WhatsApp API Config Panel\n\n---\n\n### \u2705 Tech Stack (Prefe